adline\":\"Como a Maria Mendes Massagens passou de invisível no Google a #1 da sua zona\",\"description\":\"Como a Maria Mendes Massagens passou de invisível no Google a #1 da sua zona\",\"about\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Maria Mendes Massagens\"},\"articleSection\":\"SEO Local \\u0026 Landing Page\",\"url\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio/maria-mendes-massagens\",\"inLanguage\":\"pt-PT\",\"author\":{\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/#business\"},\"publisher\":{\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/#business\"},\"creator\":{\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/#business\"},\"isPartOf\":{\"@id\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/#website\"},\"keywords\":\"Maria Mendes Massagens, SEO Local \\u0026 Landing Page, SEO local \\u0026 otimização Google, Criação de Websites \\u0026 Landing Pages, Massagens \\u0026 bem-estar · Serviço local, Element Group, agência digital Portugal, portfolio\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-01-01\",\"dateCreated\":\"2026-01-01\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-01-01\",\"image\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/Projetos/mariamendes/mariamendespc.png\"}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Início\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Portefólio\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Maria Mendes Massagens\",\"item\":\"https://elementgroup.pt/portfolio/maria-mendes-massagens\"}]}</script><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-bg pt-32 pb-16 px-6\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[640px] h-[640px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 70% 25%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.16), transparent 60%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 min-h-[44px] text-sm text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors mb-10\" href=\"/portfolio\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\">←</span> Portefólio</a><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent/90 mb-4\">SEO Local &amp; Landing Page<!-- --> · <!-- -->2026</p><h1 class=\"text-white tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.06]\">Como a Maria Mendes Massagens passou de invisível no Google a #1 da sua zona</h1><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl\">Um serviço de massagens de relaxamento em São Romão (Seia), sem site e invisível no Google. O ponto de partida: ser encontrada por quem procura na zona, no momento exato da decisão.</p><div class=\"mt-9 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5 sm:gap-4\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.05] p-3 sm:p-5 shadow-[0_0_30px_-12px_rgb(var(--accent-rgb)/0.6)]\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.6), transparent)\"></span><div class=\"font-heading text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">#1</div><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs sm:text-[12px] text-muted leading-snug\">no Google para «massagens são romão»</p></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.05] p-3 sm:p-5 shadow-[0_0_30px_-12px_rgb(var(--accent-rgb)/0.6)]\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.6), transparent)\"></span><div class=\"font-heading text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">Top 1</div><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs sm:text-[12px] text-muted leading-snug\">no Google Maps da zona</p></div><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.05] p-3 sm:p-5 shadow-[0_0_30px_-12px_rgb(var(--accent-rgb)/0.6)]\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.6), transparent)\"></span><div class=\"font-heading text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">Esgotada</div><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs sm:text-[12px] text-muted leading-snug\">agenda cheia até setembro de 2026</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><div class=\"relative h-[300px] sm:h-[380px] lg:h-[480px] overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a1d24] via-[#131417] to-[#0F0F0E]\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-24 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[460px] h-[460px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.18), transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 p-5 sm:p-8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-[360px] rounded-xl bg-white shadow-[0_20px_44px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] p-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3.5\"><span class=\"font-heading text-[15px] font-medium leading-none tracking-tight select-none\"><span style=\"color:#4285F4\">G</span><span style=\"color:#EA4335\">o</span><span style=\"color:#FBBC05\">o</span><span style=\"color:#4285F4\">g</span><span style=\"color:#34A853\">l</span><span style=\"color:#EA4335\">e</span></span><div class=\"flex-1 flex items-center gap-2 h-7 rounded-full border border-[#dfe1e5] px-3\"><span class=\"text-[11.5px] text-[#3c4043] truncate\">massagens são romão</span><svg class=\"ml-auto shrink-0\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox