eading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">#1</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">no Google para «massagens são romão»</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.06] p-4 lg:p-5 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">Top 1</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">no Google Maps da zona</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-accent/25 bg-accent/[0.06] p-4 lg:p-5 text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-heading text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-medium text-white leading-none tabular-nums\">Esgotada</div><p class=\"mt-1.5 text-[12px] text-accent\">agenda cheia até setembro de 2026</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-20 px-6\"><figure class=\"relative max-w-[820px] mx-auto overflow-hidden rounded-[24px] border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#16191f] to-[#0d0e12] p-8 md:p-10 shadow-[0_30px_70px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9),inset_0_1px_0_rgb(255_255_255/0.05)]\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute -top-14 -left-14 w-52 h-52 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.18), transparent 65%)\"></div><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative block font-heading text-5xl leading-none text-accent/55\">“</span><blockquote class=\"relative -mt-2 text-white font-heading font-medium text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.01em]\">Desde a primeira abordagem até ao conceito que pretendia foi super rápido e o trabalho realizado com excelência e muito profissionalismo. Recomendo. Serviço premium. Obrigado!</blockquote><figcaption class=\"relative mt-8 flex items-center gap-3.5\"><img alt=\"Maria Mendes\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-11 h-11 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover border border-white/15\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzkxmotwtrblluqcahnpc.supabase.co%2Fstorage%2Fv1%2Fobject%2Fpublic%2FAvatars%2520Reviews%2Fmaria-mendes.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzkxmotwtrblluqcahnpc.supabase.co%2Fstorage%2Fv1%2Fobject%2Fpublic%2FAvatars%2520Reviews%2Fmaria-mendes.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzkxmotwtrblluqcahnpc.supabase.co%2Fstorage%2Fv1%2Fobject%2Fpublic%2FAvatars%2520Reviews%2Fmaria-mendes.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"min-w-0\"><span class=\"block text-white font-medium text-sm leading-tight\">Maria Mendes</span><span class=\"block text-muted text-[13px] leading-tight\">Fundadora · Maria Mendes Massagens</span></span><a href=\"https://share.google/yHF8iJo8yG6J85Ybv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ml-auto shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 min-h-[44px] text-[12px] text-accent hover:text-white transition-colors\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 11v2.9h4.1c-.18 1.07-1.27 3.14-4.1 3.14A4.54 4.54 0 0 1 12 7.5c1.28 0 2.14.55 2.63 1.02l1.9-1.83A6.9 6.9 0 0 0 12 4.6a7.4 7.4 0 1 0 0 14.8c4.27 0 7.1-3 7.1-7.23 0-.49-.05-.86-.12-1.23L12 11Z\"></path></svg><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Ver no Google</span><span class=\"sr-only\">Ver no Google</span></a></figcaption></figure><div class=\"mt-10 flex justify-center\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Quero resultados assim para o meu negócio</span></a></div></section><section class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 py-16 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-[1000px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-dark mb-5 text-center\">Serviços usados neste projeto</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3\"><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-pill border border-white/10 bg-bg-card px-5 py-3 min-h-[44px] text-sm text-white/90 hover:border-accent/50 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/servicos/seo\">SEO local &amp; otimização Google<span class=\"text-accent transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-pill border border-white/10 bg-bg-card px-5 py-3 min-h-[44px] text-sm text-white/90 hover:border-accent/50 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/servicos/web\">Criação de Websites &amp; Landing Pages<span class=\"text-accent transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-bg to-[#08090b] border-t border-white/10 py-24 px-6\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bottom-0 w-[760px] h-[420px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgb(var(--accent-rgb) / 0.20), transparent 70%)\"></div><div class=\"relative max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px);transition:opacity 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s, transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.44,0,0.56,1) 0s;will-change:opacity, transform\"><p class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-dark mb-5\">O próximo passo</p><h2 class=\"text-white\">Tens um desafio parecido? Vamos falar.</h2><p class=\"mt-5 text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto\">Conta-me o que precisas — respondo pessoalmente em menos de 2 horas, sem compromisso.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-5\"><a class=\"nova-btn font-body \" href=\"/contacto\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__glow\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__ring\"></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"nova-btn__shine\"></span><span class=\"nova-btn__label\">Pedir